verbose_text: A recent study in 207 RA patients showed that the combination therapy of TwHF and methotrexate led to a 1.6 fold increase of ACR50 response rate than methotrexate monotherapy (76.8% vs 46.4%), further suggesting the beneficial effect of TwHF in the treatment of RA [XREF_BIBR].
